  "content": {
    "visible_text": "Quarks Class Schedule Quarks classes are open to all experience levels. Beginners and new students are always welcome, and your first week of classes is free! Please let us know you are coming by scheduling an orientation and trial class using this quick form . Schedule All Quarks classes are held in-person only. Class will take place: Monday:        4:15–5:00pm Wednesday:  4:15–5:00pm Wednesday:  5:00–5:15pm (Quarks Yellow Belt+) Friday:            4:00–4:45pm Saturday        9:30-10:15am A minimum of 2x/week attendance is required, and all students start with a mandatory orientation meeting with Master Evans, where one guardian must be present. Sign up for Quarks classes here! Reviews Facebook Community Dojo Quantum Martial Arts is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit in the State of California, and we thrive on the generosity of people like you. All donations are tax-deductible. Quantum’s tax ID number is 26-1534597. No donation is too small, or too large. Whether it’s $20 or $20,000, every cent will be hugely appreciated and put to good use. Support Our Kids Donate now to support our youth scholarship program which allows families in need to train at reduced cost. We believe investment in our community involves investing in our youth. Our Sister Schools Our Seattle Dojo has served thousands of students since opening on Capitol Hill in 1995, and currently offers youth and adult classes in the Central District. Our Portland Dojo was established in 2020, and currently offers youth and adult classes in Southeast Portland. A WordPress.com Website .",
